/Rect [ 59.9998 166.669 553.331 474.668 ]
/Subtype /Widget
/F 4
/P 478 0 R
/T (item51)
/V (This SAR is being filed regarding suspicious activity involving Acme LLC\054 a medium\055risk import\057export business\054 which was discovered on March 5\054 2026\056 The suspicious conduct involved a cash deposit of \044901\05600 made on the same day\054 which raised concerns due to its low amount\054 potentially indicating structuring behavior to avoid reporting thresholds\056 The transaction was completed\054 and the supporting documentation includes transaction records from Example Community Bank\054 where the account is held\056 The financial benefit from this transaction is unclear\054 as the origin and destination accounts remain unknown\056 The subject declined to provide an explanation for the large cash deposits\054 which raises further suspicion\056 There is no evidence of a cover\055up or attempts to deceive regulators noted in the records\056 The activity took place at the bank\047s New York branch\056 Given the potential for money laundering and fraud\054 further investigation by law enforcement is recommended\056 No information was excluded from this report\056 Acme LLC has a history of prior SAR filings\054 indicating that this may not be an isolated incident\056 There is no related litigation currently identified\054 and the transaction involved U\056S\056 currency\056 The bank\047s financial intelligence unit maintains all records related to this SAR\056)
/DA (\057HeBo 9 Tf 0 g)
/FT /Tx
/Type /Annot
/Ff 4096
/AP <<
/N 768 0 R
>>
